.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, water
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, video-games
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, apricot
House: townhouse, palace
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, january
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, rowing
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, snowmobile
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
3. the townhouse house is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
5. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | water       | coffee     |
| Hobby         | video-games | reading    |
| Food           | apricot   | pineapple |
| House   | townhouse     | palace     |
| Birthday           | march     | january      |
| Sport         | cycling     | rowing     |
| Transport     | snowmobile  | car        |

